summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Lots 32 and 33, Block 4, Brookside Addition to Lake Forest; Government Lot 1 in Section 25, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Tract 18, Assessor's Plat of Carleton Highlands; Lot 3, King County Short Plat No. 479018, as recorded under King County Recording No. 7908140953; Lot 8, Block 27, Lake Forest Park 2nd Addition; Parcels A & C of Short Plat No. 9002117, as recorded under King County Recording No. 9111080206; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
